query:
INSERT INTO supplierUsers (
  userId,
  supplierId,
  role,
  createdAt
) 
SELECT 
  u.id,
  s.id,
  'supplier_admin',
  NOW()
FROM users u, suppliers s
WHERE u.email = 'testsupplier@example.com'
  AND s.contactEmail = 'testsupplier@example.com'
